        "TileImage": "$($repository e0143799-7291-4e70-b761-3f960bf99a42).Image",
        "Description": "47,\r\rI&apos;m dying, 47. They put me in this place to &quot;heal&quot; me, but I&apos;m beyond repair. I think four men here are plotting to kill me. Return the favor to them. Just don&apos;t do anything else. I&apos;m in surgery under the name of Erich Soders, so KAI must be kept on. You wouldn&apos;t think of turning it off, would you? Right? RIGHT?\r\rYour Dearest Friend,\rL",
